http://www.myrecipes.com/recipe/sausage-bean-spinach-dip
"1  sweet onion, diced","1  red bell pepper, diced","1  (1-lb.) package hot ground pork sausage","2  garlic cloves, minced","1 teaspoon chopped fresh thyme","1/2 cup dry white wine","1  (8-oz.) package cream cheese, softened","1  (6-oz.) package fresh baby spinach, coarsely chopped","1/4 teaspoon salt","1  (15-oz.) can pinto beans, drained and rinsed","1/2 cup (2 oz.) shredded Parmesan cheese","  Serve with: Corn chip scoops, red bell pepper strips, pretzel rods"